{ IPv6 #ipv6

  It seems that Hadoop needs → development/networking/IP#ipv6 to be → Linux/networking/IPv6#disable[disabled]:
    → http://wiki.apache.org/hadoop/HadoopIPv6,
    → https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-6056

}

{ Applications go to data, not the other way round

  With big amounts of data, it would be too expensive to move the data to the application.
  It's less expensive to move the application to the nodes that contain the dat

}

